- 'swimming in the stream of better deals' metaphorically refers to customers who are getting better offers or deals;
- 'turbulent waters of pending quotes' metaphorically describes the unpredictable situation of quotes that are still under consideration and not yet finalized;
- 'insurance giant 'XYZ Insurance'' refers to the well-known insurance company XYZ Insurance;
- 'showcasing more quotes and better rates' indicates that these customers have both a higher number of quotes and more favorable insurance rates.

sql:
SELECT ABS(ROUND(AVG(premium)))
FROM policies
WHERE policy_status = 'active';

SELECT quote_id, car_id 
FROM quotes 
WHERE quote_id = 1;
